languages.text: "Соседка снова в гости зовет... Может, посвататься? Она работящая и собой недурна".

languages.text: "Next door has invited me over again... Maybe I should ask her to marry me. She's a hard worker and not a bad-looking woman."

languages.text: «La vecina me ha vuelto a invitar a su casa... A lo mejor debería pedirle que se case conmigo. Es trabajadora y no precisamente desagradable a la vista».
languages.original_text: "Next door has invited me over again... Maybe I should ask her to marry me. She's a hard worker and not a bad-looking woman."

traits.locale_text: «La vecina me ha vuelto a invitar a su casa... A lo mejor debería pedirle que se case conmigo. Es trabajadora y no precisamente desagradable a la vista».

languages.text: 「隣からまた招待された…もう、結婚を申し込むべきかもしれない。彼女は働き者だし、見た目も悪くない」
languages.original_text: "Next door has invited me over again... Maybe I should ask her to marry me. She's a hard worker and not a bad-looking woman."

traits.locale_text: 「隣からまた招待された…もう、結婚を申し込むべきかもしれない。彼女は働き者だし、見た目も悪くない」

languages.text: “隔壁的姑娘又邀请我过去了……或许我应该向她求婚才对。她干活是把好手，而且长得也不错。”
languages.original_text: "Next door has invited me over again... Maybe I should ask her to marry me. She's a hard worker and not a bad-looking woman."

traits.locale_text: “隔壁的姑娘又邀请我过去了……或许我应该向她求婚才对。她干活是把好手，而且长得也不错。”

languages.text: "Meine Nachbarin hat mich schon wieder eingeladen ... Vielleicht sollte ich sie bitten, mich zu heiraten. Sie ist eine hart arbeitende Frau und sieht nicht schlecht aus."
languages.original_text: "Next door has invited me over again... Maybe I should ask her to marry me. She's a hard worker and not a bad-looking woman."

traits.locale_text: "Meine Nachbarin hat mich schon wieder eingeladen ... Vielleicht sollte ich sie bitten, mich zu heiraten. Sie ist eine hart arbeitende Frau und sieht nicht schlecht aus."

languages.text: « La voisine m'a encore invité à dîner... Peut-être que je devrais la demander en mariage. Elle n'est pas vilaine, et le travail ne lui fait pas peur. »
languages.original_text: "Next door has invited me over again... Maybe I should ask her to marry me. She's a hard worker and not a bad-looking woman."

languages.text: "Yan komşu beni yine davet etti... Belki de ona evlilik teklif etmeliyim. Sıkı çalışıyor ve görüntüsü de hiç fena değil."
